.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db

# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
*.cab
*.msi
*.msm
*.msp

# Linux
*~

